	<strong>About Us:</strong></p>
<p>
	Drumbi is in need of people who are willing to perform above the fold, for nothing more then the satisfaction of changing conversations around the world. We&rsquo;re turning an average phone call into a delightful experience for both the customer and the business.</p>
<p>
	We love to work extremely hard, but we also like to play when given the right opportunity. If there is a listing here that doesn&rsquo;t fit your liking, please message us and convince us that we need you &mdash; We&rsquo;ll be listening.</p>
<p>
	<strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<p>
	As the VP of Engineering you will lead a team in research, architecture, and development of telephony technology and will report directly to the CTO. You will have the opportunity to create and enhance products on top of our existing platform that will support scale and growth. The candidate should have meticulous focus and strong technical knowledge that will help in delivering quality products on time. The VP will have direct influence over product roadmaps, and should be well versed in a diverse set of programming languages.</p>
<p>
